.TH SINGINE-ARCHETYPE 1 "2026-03-21" "singine 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
singine-archetype \- list and materialize higher-level reusable Singine archetypes
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B singine archetype list
[\fB--json\fR]
.PP
.B singine archetype materialize
\fINAME\fR
\fB--output-dir\fR \fIPATH\fR
[\fB--title\fR \fITEXT\fR]
[\fB--json\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B singine archetype
is the focused alias for the higher-level reusable entries in the Singine
template library. It is intended for bundle-style outputs rather than small
project skeletons.
.PP
Current built-ins include:
.IP \(bu 2
\fBpersonal-os-essay\fR
.IP \(bu 2
\fBplatform-blueprint\fR
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --output-dir \fIPATH\fR
Destination directory for the materialized archetype bundle.
.TP
.B --title \fITEXT\fR
Optional title override passed through when the selected archetype supports it.
.TP
.B --json
Emit the resulting payload as JSON.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
singine archetype list --json

singine archetype materialize personal-os-essay \\
  --output-dir /tmp/singine-personal-os \\
  --json

singine archetype materialize platform-blueprint \\
  --output-dir /tmp/singine-platform-blueprint \\
  --json
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR singine (1),
.BR singine-template (1),
.BR singine-man (1),
.BR singine-essay (1),
.BR singine-platform (1)
